so the information about how to make your decisions

121
00:04:49,446 --> 00:04:50,426
really doesn't exist yet.

122
00:04:50,426 --> 00:04:51,807
You are creating that information.

123
00:04:53,009 --> 00:04:57,930
The other time there's lots of ambiguity is when we're personally doing something that we've never done before

