1068
00:44:52,551 --> 00:44:54,171
and it'll force you to put some things at the top

1069
00:44:54,171 --> 00:44:54,852
and other things at the bottom.

1070
00:44:54,852 --> 00:44:56,632
Okay, so in conclusion, to ship your game,

1071
00:44:56,632 --> 00:45:00,734
you have to recognize ambiguity and you have to reduce it.

1072
00:45:00,734 --> 00:45:03,755
You cannot ship until you've gotten rid

1073
00:45:03,755 --> 00:45:05,456
of all of the ambiguity on your project.

1074
00:45:07,398 --> 00:45:10,940
Second, ambiguity is something that negatively affects all of us,

1075
00:45:10,940 --> 00:45:13,341
and the producers who can deal with it effectively

1076
00:45:13,341 --> 00:45:14,021
are going to be the most valuable.

1077
00:45:14,021 --> 00:45:16,642
Your job is to make sure that you have a plan

1078
00:45:16,642 --> 00:45:18,943
that drives down ambiguity at the right time

1079
00:45:18,943 --> 00:45:20,724
and lets you successfully ship a great game.

1080
00:45:20,724 --> 00:45:23,105
And even though ambiguity can cause a bunch of problems on your game,

1081
00:45:23,105 --> 00:45:24,185
you can fix them.

